item.title: Orb view teleports
item.dc:creator: @Steve734 Steve734
item.description:
@Steve734 wrote:

Okay, what you want to do, is go into clickingmost.java in your server files.

Then hit ctrl + f. Then search Pest Ctrl.
There should be an empty space below Pest Ctrl, Then go down a couple lines, and there should be another empty space below Pest Ctrl.

Then hit ctrl + f again. Search c.triggerTele(3428, 3537, 0); and then you will see this.

Go under c.resetfollowers(); and paste this code.

if(c.interfaceGame == 2) c.triggerTele(####, ####, 0); c.killMyNPCs(); c.resetfollowers();

Replace the #'s with your X and Y Coordinates that you want to teleport to. (Where ever your God Wars is.)

And thats about all there is to it.

Please give proper credits to me if you use this.
